a major star in America?

01:18:36.800 --> 01:18:37.920
[George chuckles]

01:18:38.680 --> 01:18:42.000
[Andrew] It was proper superstar status.

01:18:43.640 --> 01:18:45.400
We'd broken America.

01:18:47.320 --> 01:18:49.560
-Good night! Thank you!
-[crowd cheering]

