that you two may separate,

01:21:39.000 --> 01:21:41.800
go opposite directions.
Can you foresee such a time, Andrew?

01:21:41.880 --> 01:21:44.040
-Such a time? There'll be a time, yeah.
-Mm.

01:21:46.680 --> 01:21:49.840
