What's it like to play your last concert?

01:24:00.400 --> 01:24:02.520
-We're excited.
-We'll let you know afterwards.

01:24:02.600 --> 01:24:04.480
-Yeah!
-[reporter] Any regrets?

01:24:04.560 --> 01:24:06.960
None whatsoever.
Huge thank you to everyone…

01:24:07.040 --> 01:24:09.920
Not only today,
but for the last four years.

01:24:10.520 --> 01:24:11.520
-All right.
-Thanks a lot.

01:24:11.600 --> 01:24:12.440
Cheers.

